title: House Hunters: Comedians on Couches
overview: In a star-studded special event, America's favorite contactless past time—watching and commenting on House Hunters—gets a fun new twist when a celebrity lineup led by Dan Levy and Natasha Leggero deliver hilarious, no holds barred, color commentary on classic episodes of the hit series in House Hunters: Comedians on Couches. Together via videoconference, the entertainers will call out the victories and agonizing defeats caused by paint colors, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and open concept spaces.
